dcterms:description: A de-identified warehouse of over 2.2 million electronic health records (EHRs) from Vanderbilt University Medical Center, containing various types of data including demographics, ICD-9 codes, CPT-4 codes, BMI, and blood pressure readings.
dcterms:title: VUMC Synthetic Derivative (SD)

dcterms:description: A refined version of the VUMC Synthetic Derivative dataset, containing 770,231 records after removing noise and ensuring data quality, including constraints on vital signs.
dcterms:title: CSD (Clean Synthetic Derivative)
